<p>One simple solution, is obviously to turn off â€œOpen Safe Filesâ€ in Safari, but that does make life a bit more difficult, so, for those who want to have their cake and eat it too (at least on this issue) I found it blindingly easy to add what I think should be closer to the default behavior - and itâ€™s not dependent on Safari.</p>

